Scenario: Serialize Credit Authorization XML
Given I have a XmlSerializer for Credit Authorization
When I have an Credit Authorization xml:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="Shift_JIS"?>
<CreditAuthorization>
   <corpid>0000000000</corpid>
   <storeid>000031</storeid>
   <terminalid>0999</terminalid>
   <txid>0001</txid>
   <txdatetime>20110930113045</txdatetime>
  <amount>2000</amount>
   <pan>5250123456789012</pan>
   <expirationdate>1012</expirationdate>   
</CreditAuthorization>
Then I should get Credit Authorization:
|amount|corpid|expirationdate|pan|storeid|terminalid|txdatetime|txid|
|2000|0000000000|1012|5250123456789012|000031|0999|20110930113045|0001|

When I have an empty Credit Authorization xml
Then I should get empty Credit Authorization
